Scenes From the Democratic Marriage ( https://puck.news/elon-musk-is-showin=
g-himself-to-be-a-soft-target-for-democrats/?utm_campaign=3DThe+Best+%26+Th=
e+Brightest+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F23%2F25%29&utm_content=3DThe+Best+%26+The+=
Brightest+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F23%2F25%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_sou=
